-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
GETTING STARTED:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Please see the install/ directory and its README file for all information
concerning required dependencies and installation instructions.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
RUNNING THE SCRIPT:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./run.sh <path_to_git_dir>

(Use "./run.sh -help" for complete usage instructions)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TEST FRAMEWORK:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
All automatic tests are located in test/test.sh - this includes automatic
integration and unit tests.

The test script is executed by running the command:
    test/test.sh

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------   
MANUAL TESTS:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Analyzer:
Check Over format of Analyzer/commits.txt file after running automatic tests.
The file should be of the form:

gitstats
%       2007-07-30
self    8
write   0
commits 4
author  8
lines   7
...
